飓风季的实际活跃度低于预期，5月25日至11月5日间共计成14个热带低气压，其中半数增强成热带风暴，但只有六场获命名<ref name="MWR">{{cite journal | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | author = Robert A. Case and Harold P. Gerrish | journal = Monthly Weather Review | publisher = American Meteorological Society | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | date = 1988-04 | volume = 116 | issue = 4 | pages = 939–949 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1987 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1988)116<0939:AHSO>2.0.CO;2 | format = PDF | bibcode = 1988MWRv..116..939C | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040405/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，第二号热带低气压是在飓风季过后重新分析时才升级成热带风暴，所以没有名称。[[1987年飓风阿琳|热带风暴阿琳]]、[[1987年飓风艾米莉|艾米莉]]和[[1987年飓风弗洛伊德|弗洛伊德]]都增强至飓风标准，但只有艾米莉成为大型飓风。<ref name="Seasonalactivity-3">{{cite news | author = The Frederick Post | date = 1988-06-02 | title = Hurricane Death Toll May Be Much Higher | newspaper = The Frederick Post}}</ref>

美国在本季一共受到四个热带气旋影响，其中三个先后吹袭[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]，另有未获命名的热带风暴袭击[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]并对[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸]]大部分地区构成影响<ref name="Seasonalactivity-1">{{cite news | author=The Advocate | date = 1987-12-01 | title = Hurricane season ends; U.S. gets break in '87 | newspaper = The Advocate}}</ref><ref name="Seasonalactivity-2">{{cite web | author = Fort Lauderdale News & Sun-Sentinel | date = 1987-12-01 | title = Slow '87 Hurricane Season Coming To A Quiet Close | newspaper = Fort Lauderdale News & Sun-Sentinel | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=DM&p_theme=dm&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0ED3CF7CC988C5DF&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820165759/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=DM&p_theme=dm&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0ED3CF7CC988C5DF&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>

这年飓风季的活跃程度也通过累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]的低迷反映出来，只有34<ref>{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，属“低于正常水平”范围<ref name="background">{{cite web | author = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/outlooks/background_information.shtml | title = Background information: the North Atlantic Hurricane Season | date = 2010-05-27 | publisher = Climate Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-04-14 | archivedate = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203030732/http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/outlooks/background_information.shtml }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

