8月8日，[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]近海一片基本保持静止的[[冷锋|冷锋]]末端关联的低气压天气系统组织成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带低气压]]，并朝南面飘移<ref name="ArleneTCRPg1">{{cite report | author = Harrold P. Gerrish | date = 1987-10-10 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Arlene – Page 1 – Storm History I | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180027/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim01.gif | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[对流|对流]]逐渐组织，气旋于8月10日在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空成为第三号热带低气压。低气压的移动路线形成反气旋环路，转朝东北前进。根据[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机的报告，气象机构估计气旋于8月11日达到热带风暴标准。受[[高压脊|高压脊]]产生的气流影响，阿琳总体保持向东面移动，在此期间还两次转向南下，但整体仍是在朝东北前进。<ref name="ArleneTCRPg1" />气旋发展起初受到[[百慕大|百慕大]]附近的[[低压槽|低压槽]]制约，无法显著强化，但在东面的高气压影响下北上后，风暴因外界环境更为有利而增强，于8月22日成为飓风<ref name="ArleneTCRPg2">{{cite report | author = Harrold P. Gerrish | date = 1987-10-10 | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Arlene – Page 2 – Storm History II, Meteorological Statistics, Impact and Conclusion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230649/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/arlene/prelim02.gif }}</ref>。不过，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]早在两天前就根据卫星图像上的[[风眼|眼状特征]]把风暴升级。成为飓风后，阿琳加速向东北方向进入北大西洋的寒冷水域上空，于8月23日在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]和爱尔兰中途附近洋面转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。温带残留转向东南，之后又朝东面移动，最终登陆[[伊比利亚半岛|伊比利亚半岛]]后于8月28日在西班牙上空逐渐消散。<ref name="ArleneTCRPg2" />

随着阿琳逼近，百慕大居民接到警报，预计风速会达到每小时80公里，建议众人关紧窗户<ref name="Arlene-News1">{{cite news | author = The Miami Herald | date = 1987-08-13 | title = Bermuda Boards Up For Arlene | newspaper = The Miami Herald | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CA760B4795&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210120094249/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367CA760B4795&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。最终岛上的持续风速约为每小时60公里，阵风时速达到80公里<ref name="ArleneTCRPg2" />。一名盲人水手因受阿琳影响无法继续完成独自穿越大西洋的目标，船体在海上受损，不得不赶往百慕大港口躲避<ref name="Arlene-News2">{{cite news | author = The Atlanta Journal and The Atlanta Constitution | date = 1987-08-13 | title = Blind sailor to ride out storm at sea | newspaper = The Atlanta Journal and The Atlanta Constitution | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=AT&p_theme=at&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB7C2D79EA3903E&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820165846/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=AT&p_theme=at&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB7C2D79EA3903E&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴还在西班牙临海地区产生中等程度降水，[[罗塔_(加的斯省)|罗塔]]的降雨量打破8月历史纪录<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="ArleneTCRPg2" />。风暴从最初成型至达到飓风强度共计费时14.5天，创下大西洋飓风的新纪录<ref name="hurdat">{{cite report | author = NHC Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track | publisher = NOAA | date = 2006-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyhurdat_5105.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202544/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyhurdat_5105.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
