[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]北部的一个上层气旋在美国东南近海发展，佛罗里达州东侧的低气压区周围有对流逐渐组织，于9月7日成为本季第九号热带低气压。气旋起初杂乱无章，<ref name="TD9-4">{{cite news | author = Chicago Sun-Times | date = 1987-09-08 | title = Tropical depression forms off South Carolina | newspaper = Chicago Sun-Times | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36D852CE940E1&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105110034/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36D852CE940E1&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>总体保持北上趋势且未有增强，很快就沿南卡罗莱纳州海岸登陆。低气压穿越[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]和[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]，于9月10日进入[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]上空的锋面天气系统。气旋沿途普降中雨，并以[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]中部降雨量最高，达到260毫米。[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]、南卡罗莱纳州、北卡罗莱纳州和[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]的气象站都测得超过125毫米雨量。<ref name="TD9-Rains">{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression 9 Rainfall Summary | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075336/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//td9of1987.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td9of1987.html | date =  }}</ref>。面对降雨威胁，部分地点发布山洪警报，弗吉尼亚州有超过50条道路被冲毁<ref name="TD9-4_2">{{cite news | author = The Miami Herald | date = 1987-09-09 | title = Depression Weakens Over North Carolina | newspaper = The Miami Herald | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367EC885EC5B0&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105110118/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB367EC885EC5B0&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。湿滑的路面导致[[495号州际公路_(首都环线)|首都环线]]上三公里路段内有三辆牵引车发生事故，牵引车厢同汽车其他部位相撞。此外，有四人被水流暴涨的溪流所困，需要外界救援。<ref name="TD9-5">{{cite web | author = Eve Zibart | date = 1987-09-09 | title = Rain-Slicked Beltway Spawns Wrecks and Traffic Tie-Ups | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/washingtonpost/doc/306946745.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=SEP%2009,%201987&author=Eve%20Zibart&pub=The%20Washington%20Post&edition=&startpage=&desc=Rain-Slicked%20Beltway%20Spawns%20Wrecks%20and%20Traffic%20Tie-Ups | archive-date = 2017-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171025121441/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/washingtonpost/doc/306946745.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=SEP%2009%2C%201987&author=Eve%20Zibart&pub=The%20Washington%20Post&edition=&startpage=&desc=Rain-Slicked%20Beltway%20Spawns%20Wrecks%20and%20Traffic%20Tie-Ups | dead-url = no }}</ref>
