{{Main|1987年飓风艾米莉}}
本季第十号热带低气压于9月20日成型，并且当天就在南美洲近海增强成热带风暴。艾米莉快速强化，不足48小时后就于9月22日晚达到飓风标准。<ref name="EmilyTCR7">{{cite report | author = Harrold P. Gerrish | date = 1987-11-12 | title = Hurricane Emily Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 7 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim07.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184048/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim07.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>

气旋接下来缓慢转向北上并且很快就登陆[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]，夺走三条人命并导致价值3000万美元的破坏。风暴从[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]上空经过，然后转向东北并登陆百慕大，引起价值5000万美元的破坏，但没有造成人员遇难。<ref name="EmilyTCR4">{{cite report | author = Harrold P. Gerrish | date = 1987-11-12 | title = Hurricane Emily Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 4 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim04.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223012/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim04.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>飓风登陆后降级成热带风暴，其最高风速为每小时205公里，已达三级飓风标准，是本季唯一的[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]<ref name="EmilyTCR7" />。

艾米莉此后达到风力时速140公里的第二波强度高峰，最终于9月26日消散<ref name="EmilyTCR7" />。成千上万的候鸟在风暴期间飞到百慕大躲避，其中包括约一万只[[食米鸟|食米鸟]]和数千只[[灰喉地莺|灰喉地莺]]。经过百慕大后，风暴成为20世纪移动速度第二快的飓风，前进速度高达每小时105公里，相当于每秒31米，仅次于[[1938年新英格兰飓风|1938年新英格兰飓风]]。此外，艾米莉还是1981年的[[1981年飓风卡特里娜|飓风卡特里娜]]过后[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的首场飓风。<ref name="EmilyTCR1">{{cite report | author = Harrold P. Gerrish | date = 1987-11-12 | title = Hurricane Emily Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175946/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim01.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>
