{{Main|1987年飓风弗洛伊德}}
10月9日，[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]近海一片广阔的低气压区组织成热带低气压。气旋向东南飘移，之后转向[[罗盘方位|西北偏北]]，于10月10日成为热带风暴并获名“弗洛伊德”（{{lang|en|Floyd}}）。风暴随后经过古巴西部，然后加速朝东北前进，于10月12日晚升级成飓风。弗洛伊德经过[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]，外界大气环境因基本保持静止的锋区影响变得干燥而寒冷。<ref name="FloydTCR1">{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim01.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>风暴[[对流|对流]]变得非常混乱，于10月13日在[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]东南方向降级成热带风暴，经过巴哈马后，弗洛伊德转变成温带气旋，最终于10月14日被锋面天气系统吸收<ref name="FloydTCR2">{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 2 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090102/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。

由于飓风组织结构杂乱无章，佛罗里达州遭受的破坏程度很轻。全州的最高降雨量达到256毫米，该州南部的农作物受到中等程度破坏。<ref name="FloydRain">{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2007 | title = Hurricane Floyd – October 10–13, 1987 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161003055324/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//floyd1987.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/floyd1987.html | archivedate = 2016-10-03 | date =  }}</ref><ref name="FloydTCR3" />此外，气旋还催生出[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，对佛罗里达礁岛群部分地点构成破坏。风暴造成的经济损失总额约为50万美元，没有导致人员伤亡。<ref name="FloydTCR3">{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 3 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim03.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002022441/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>
