{{Main|1987年第十四号热带低气压}}
10月下旬，加勒比海中部有大范围低气压区存在。系统稳步组织，于10月31日成为第十四号热带低气压。气旋朝西北移动，行经海域因高气压系统末端的上层低气压区影响而存在大量风切变。到了11月1日，热带低气压的强度已经很弱，其中残留的对流也很少。气旋转向北上穿越古巴，然后经对流爆发重新组织，于11月2日经过佛罗里达礁岛群并产生强烈阵风。<ref name="FourteenTCR1">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-17 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 1 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173937/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>气旋继续向西北偏北前进，路线与佛罗里达州西海岸基本平行，但大部分对流都在11月3日消亡。低气压转向东北，于11月4日同佛罗里达州北部上空的弱温带低气压区合并。<ref name="FourteenTCR2">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-17 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 2 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000241/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim02.gif }}</ref>

北面远至乔治亚州和南卡罗莱纳州最南端都出现降水，但这些位置雨量不高，[[美国东南部|东南部]]其他地区降下中到大雨<ref name="TD14-Rains">{{cite report | author = David Roth | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression 14 Rainfalls | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075213/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td141987.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td141987.html | date =  }}</ref>。气旋产生的降水在牙买加引发重大破坏，导致六人遇难<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="FourteenTCR4">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-17 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Tropical Cyclone Report – Page 4 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220500/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim04.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/trop/prelim04.gif }}</ref>。
